As #LosAngeles expands #COVID19 #vaccine eligibility, a reminder that eligibility does not equal #access. 

Only a third of seniors in some LA communities are #vaccinated

While we must vaccinate as quickly as possible, speed does not have to come at the cost of #equity https://t.co/NqHZ9lzAZP https://t.co/LaCObPFxOH
